des:
HEVOLTA Mind.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off Mind.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your Mind - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your HEVOLTA products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "HEVOLTA" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register your HEVOLTA account in our "HEVOLTA" app;
(3). You need to have some HEVOLTA devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "HEVOLTA" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "HEVOLTA" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "HEVOLTA" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "HEVOLTA", and you'll be navigated to "HEVOLTA" login page;
(9). Input your HEVOLTA account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the Mind.”
“Alexa,turn off the Mind.”
Note:Mind is a thermostat
